window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Do you need my help? <br>It was always the first question he asked. <br>They called him when they had nowhere else to turn. </p> <p>Raised and trained as part of a top-secret programme, he was sent to the worst places in the world to do things his government denied any knowledge of. </p> <p>Then he broke with the programme and disappeared. But now someone's on his tail. Someone who knows he was once known simply as Orphan X. </p>"; 
